## Work In Progress
***
### My Projects
#### Projects From Courses
I'm currently building a 'social network' of sorts for my software engineering class, which can be found [here](http://cs.lafayette.edu/~cs205_2016_grp01/). It's a collaboration project with @everlastingbugstopper and Kris.

In my data structures and algorithms class, I wrote a recipe book program in java, which you can learn more about [here](https://github.com/beckmc/RecipeBook-CS150). Over the summer I made an objective-c version of it which implements a GUI and features some other changes, which can be found [here](https://github.com/beckmc/RecipeBook).
***
### Other Stuff
Sometimes I write things on Medium. You can find my profile at <https://medium.com/@mcbeckjr> and check out some of the things I have written there.
***
### Contact Me
You can get in touch with me at beckmc@lafayette.edu
